text.div:
MediaType

Whether the Media is a photo, video, or audio

This value set defines it's own terms in the system http://hl7.org/fhir/media-type

CodeDisplayDefinition
photoThe media consists of one or more unmoving images.
videoThe media consists of a series of frames that capture a moving image.
audioThe media consists of a sound recording.
